comments: Very good prof. She makes the class interesting by getting the students engaged in the material. There is quite a lot of work to be done in her class, but it\'s actually very useful work, and she will always help you if you need it.

Great prof teaches the class really really well. You will actually learn stuff applicable to the real world. Plus she brings in interesting guest speakers, and good topics to get you thinking. I definitely recommend you take her class. :D
Really really good prof. She\'s really funny and very smart. If you get her, consider yourself lucky, she has a lot to teach in this course.
